  "detailed_description": "In Armechgeddon, you are dropped into an onslaught of robotic enemies and left to fight against all odds. Collect scrap and upgrade your mech and weapons, altering their behavior to survive as long as possible. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/c93a700020f5acfb5330414cdc56d8a8.poster.avif?t=1713266744\" width=600 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/c93a700020f5acfb5330414cdc56d8a8.webm?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/c93a700020f5acfb5330414cdc56d8a8.mp4?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to Learn, Hard to Master</h2>Piloting your mech is as simple as moving and rotating to face any direction. You operate melee attacks, charging, jump jets, and a suite of overpowered weapons with just these two inputs. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/7b5711a95df06f12a553ff34ce581bc3.poster.avif?t=1713266744\" width=536 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/7b5711a95df06f12a553ff34ce581bc3.webm?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/7b5711a95df06f12a553ff34ce581bc3.mp4?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer Many Maps and Difficulties</h2>As you progress through 6 unique missions with multiple difficulty tiers, you'll unlock weapons, upgrades, pilots, and mechs. Purchase upgrades in the garage to make yourself unstoppable.  <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/91767c4cc6752be61122cb214ad987c3.poster.avif?t=1713266744\" width=608 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/91767c4cc6752be61122cb214ad987c3.webm?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/91767c4cc6752be61122cb214ad987c3.mp4?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Go for the Optimal Build!</h2>Try out 14 different mechs, 14 different pilots, and 16 passive bonuses to see how efficiently you can clear each difficulty.",
  "about_the_game": "In Armechgeddon, you are dropped into an onslaught of robotic enemies and left to fight against all odds. Collect scrap and upgrade your mech and weapons, altering their behavior to survive as long as possible. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/c93a700020f5acfb5330414cdc56d8a8.poster.avif?t=1713266744\" width=600 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/c93a700020f5acfb5330414cdc56d8a8.webm?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/c93a700020f5acfb5330414cdc56d8a8.mp4?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to Learn, Hard to Master</h2>Piloting your mech is as simple as moving and rotating to face any direction. You operate melee attacks, charging, jump jets, and a suite of overpowered weapons with just these two inputs. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/7b5711a95df06f12a553ff34ce581bc3.poster.avif?t=1713266744\" width=536 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/7b5711a95df06f12a553ff34ce581bc3.webm?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/7b5711a95df06f12a553ff34ce581bc3.mp4?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer Many Maps and Difficulties</h2>As you progress through 6 unique missions with multiple difficulty tiers, you'll unlock weapons, upgrades, pilots, and mechs. Purchase upgrades in the garage to make yourself unstoppable.  <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/91767c4cc6752be61122cb214ad987c3.poster.avif?t=1713266744\" width=608 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/91767c4cc6752be61122cb214ad987c3.webm?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1929250/extras/91767c4cc6752be61122cb214ad987c3.mp4?t=1713266744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Go for the Optimal Build!</h2>Try out 14 different mechs, 14 different pilots, and 16 passive bonuses to see how efficiently you can clear each difficulty.",
